@startuml
title findMany AST Compatibility (After)
skinparam backgroundColor #F7FAFC
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #2F3E46
skinparam defaultFontName Consolas

actor "SDK Consumer" as Consumer #B2EBF2
component "createClient(...)" as Client #D5F5E3
component "TableQueryBuilder<Row, Insert, Update, Context>" as Builder #FFF59D
component "findMany({\n  select,\n  where,\n  orderBy,\n  limit\n})" as FindMany #FFE082
component "Query AST Compiler\n- select tree -> columns string\n- where -> conditions\n- orderBy -> sort_by" as Compiler #D1C4E9
component "Typed Registry\n(relation-aware fromModel context)" as Registry #E3F2FD
component "Gateway Client" as Gateway #AED581
database "Athena HTTP Gateway" as GatewayApi #80CBC4

Consumer --> Client : from("table") / fromModel(...)
Client --> Builder : Build fluent builder
Builder --> FindMany : eager read
FindMany --> Compiler : Compile object AST
Registry --> Builder : relation-aware type context
Compiler --> Gateway : unchanged /gateway/fetch or /gateway/query payload
Gateway --> GatewayApi : HTTP request

note right of Compiler
String-based .select(...)
and SelectChain stay intact.
findMany is additive.
end note
@enduml
